### Question 💬

How to get the session inside a [Server Actions](https://nextjs.org/blog/next-13-4#server-actions-alpha)?

Show this error:

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/50633599/236581387-ce1e8a88-e913-4467-90aa-ff738f9b82c7.png)


### How to reproduce ☕️

```ts
export async function create(formData: FormData) {
  'use server';

  const session = await getServerSession();

  console.log(session);
}
```

